author: krysto2002
title: Not as good for a rare set, but it still is free
review:
First off, I did not get this through Japan, although not listed, the set was also a promo release for Florida Natural OJ, and came free at the supermarkets.

This is the blockier of the two (possibly three) sets available. The hinges are bricks and not plates like the other one, so there's one reason to dislike it. The set is hardly posable, neither of the to is... But they are still free!

This was a rather flimsy model, but aquiring it now is beyond my knowledge. Hey, it's not great, but it is still a free promo!

author: hustla187
title: Odd Dino
review: This is an interesting dinosaur that was given out back in 2004. I really don't like the silver head and the tail because it makes it less of a dinosaur. Besides, it is too flimsy anyway. This is pretty bad for a promo.
